author: mgrigorov
msg: Upgrade Apache Commons-IO FileCleaner to its latest version (renamed to FileCleaningTracker).

Since it starts a thread to do its stuff and this is not allowed in some environments (like Google AppEngine) not it is possible to disable it by using "getResourceSettings().setFileUploadCleaner(null)" in MyApp#init().
